  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join a Friend for free with Friendpass</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>King of the Hat is 2-4 player 2D party platformer where you fight with a hat! Throw your hat to attack, defend and bait opponents. But watch out! If someone jumps on your hat... you die!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In King of the Hat, your hat contains your soul. Crush your opponent’s hats (and souls) to assert your dominance over them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When you throw your hat, it goes on fire and becomes invulnerable. You can use it to beat the devil out of other players or to defend against your opponents’ flaming hats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Although the basic mechanics are easy to pick up and play, King of the Hat allows for deep, hat-tastic competitive play as a 2 player game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Change the rules, add power ups and play around level hazards to create the hat-based madness you've always dreamed of.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>King of the Hat is 2-4 player 2D party platformer where you fight with a hat! Throw your hat to attack, defend and bait opponents. But watch out! If someone jumps on your hat... you die!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In King of the Hat, your hat contains your soul. Crush your opponent’s hats (and souls) to assert your dominance over them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When you throw your hat, it goes on fire and becomes invulnerable. You can use it to beat the devil out of other players or to defend against your opponents’ flaming hats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Although the basic mechanics are easy to pick up and play, King of the Hat allows for deep, hat-tastic competitive play as a 2 player game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Change the rules, add power ups and play around level hazards to create the hat-based madness you've always dreamed of.",
